index 57892e814cd..c719241a7f5 100644
--- a/docs/devel/loads-stores.rst
+++ b/docs/devel/loads-stores.rst
@@ -235,16 +235,13 @@ Regexes for git grep:
  - ``\<cpu_ld[us]\?[bwlq]\(_[bl]e\)\?_data\>``
  - ``\<cpu_st[bwlq]\(_[bl]e\)\?_data\+\>``
 
